The paper proposes a visual servoing approach for robotic systems using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also uses optical flow and deep neural networks for feature extraction and prediction, which falls under the categories of cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also presents an extensive benchmark and evaluates the approach for real scenarios, which involves performance analysis and experimentation, making it relevant to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
